r = np.arange(0, 2, 0.01)
theta = 2 * np.pi * r
fig, ax = plt.subplots(
    subplot_kw = {"projection": "polar"}
)
ax.plot(theta, r)
ax.set_rticks([0.5, 1.0, 1.5, 2.0])
ax.grid(True)
plt.show()
